 lash · gpt-5.4
    • sent input with write_stdin
    • got echoed output
    • closed stdin cleanly

  • Delegation worked:
    • spawned a child agent
    • it inspected the temp dir
    • returned a structured result

  • Parallel wrappers worked:
  batch successfully ran multiple independent calls
